{
  "text": "Several authors have shown that increasing the concentration of photoinitiators in the material will improve the degree of cure [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . This will be only beneficial up to specific thresholds [CITATION_5] and also may increase yellowing when CQ is used [CITATION_6] [CITATION_7] .",
